Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.98,Signs,,0,0,0,,The 25 Year Old High School Girl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.98,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an1}Episode 12: I Love You!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.21,0:00:10.99,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.43,0:00:13.34,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I ignored your feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.71,0:00:14.99,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,...and hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.99,0:00:17.06,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.41,0:00:19.62,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,You followed me because you were worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.01,0:00:23.00,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for saying it was none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.41,0:00:27.40,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,When I see how you've become such a wonderful teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.40,0:00:29.86,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,it makes me angry and depressed about my current situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.86,0:00:33.01,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,and I ended up taking it out on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.81,0:00:34.44,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Natori...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:38.51,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Do you remember when you would tutor me back in high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.51,0:00:41.03,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.03,0:00:44.02,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Well, I wasn't exactly the best tutor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.25,0:00:49.93,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Even though it was for a stranger, you took it more seriously than I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.93,0:00:50.96,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I couldn't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.96,0:00:52.34,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.81,0:00:54.94,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,But seeing you like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.31,0:00:57.64,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,...I thought "that doesn't seem so bad."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.28,0:01:00.29,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.29,0:01:03.80,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,You're a big part of the reason I am where I am today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.13,0:01:07.79,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,That's why I don't want you badmouthing yourself like that in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.67,0:01:09.88,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Kanie...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.33,0:01:14.39,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,By the way, do you... really not remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.39,0:01:15.52,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,About that one time...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.89,0:01:16.88,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Which time was this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.88,0:01:18.46,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,It's just, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.29,0:01:21.39,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,...confessed to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.01,0:01:22.89,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.16,0:01:26.64,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1200,0)}Library
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.59,0:01:26.64,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Hey Natori, do you like, have a boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.05,0:01:28.72,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.05,0:01:30.88,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I'm not exactly popular with the boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.27,0:01:34.15,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I like you pretty well, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.61,0:01:38.16,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're so funny, Kanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.16,0:01:38.64,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.97,0:01:41.33,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's amazing Kanie!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.33,0:01:43.91,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,You've finished all the review problems!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.91,0:01:45.46,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.97,0:01:49.97,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I-I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.97,0:01:54.89,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Back then I was sure you didn't feel that way about me,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.89,0:01:58.78,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,so when you told me so casually, I was sure you were teasing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.11,0:02:00.89,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,It was a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.89,0:02:05.85,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,U-Umm, could it be that you... still feel that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:09.19,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I-I thought this conversation was past tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.49,0:02:12.19,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kanie's so embarrassed...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.93,0:02:14.74,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crap, he's just too cute.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.45,0:02:17.15,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.71,0:02:19.66,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I... want you to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.15,0:02:22.66,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I love you even more now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.45,0:02:26.27,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,You're crying. What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.27,0:02:30.12,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Am I? Sorry, I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.63,0:02:34.85,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Never say it's none of my business again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.85,0:02:35.42,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.87,0:02:38.77,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Also, I want you to come to me next time something happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.77,0:02:39.36,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.33,0:02:43.67,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Crap, I really want to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.67,0:02:44.63,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.63,0:02:45.38,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Don't want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.75,0:02:47.24,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I didn't say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.25,0:02:51.93,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,You look really into it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.93,0:02:53.94,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,T-That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:57.51,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Because it feels better than usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.51,0:02:59.95,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Y-You're such a tease!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:02.44,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,You only just realized that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.77,0:03:05.91,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,N-No, don't! Not... there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.99,0:03:09.36,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,W-Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.36,0:03:10.30,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:12.29,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, stop...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:14.88,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you do that now, I'm going to...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.91,0:03:19.56,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Natori?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:21.43,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:22.38,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.77,0:03:24.55,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Natori.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.55,0:03:25.79,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I can't take it any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:27.89,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I'm going to put it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.51,0:03:29.39,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.{I guess this is as close to consent as we're going to get, boys and girls.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.45,0:03:35.67,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}H-He's being so rough.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.67,0:03:39.90,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If Kanie wants to do it that way, I'll show him I can keep up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.73,0:03:44.57,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,We shouldn't be doing this here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:46.37,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,This is so embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:52.32,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I love you, Natori.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.43,0:04:06.35,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I expect to see you in school tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.89,0:04:10.14,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Save that kind of talk for your students.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.21,0:04:12.22,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.57,0:04:14.37,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Umm, K-Kanie?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.37,0:04:14.78,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.77,0:04:20.37,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,It made me really happy to hear how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.37,0:04:25.11,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I... love you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:29.68,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,What took you so long, dummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.98,0:04:48.90,Songs,,0,0,0,,Who could have predicted this reunion?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.90,0:04:57.20,Songs,,0,0,0,,I reel in this thread of memory, and use it to spin my tale
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:05:02.09,Songs,,0,0,0,,Why are you all pushy one minute,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.09,0:05:08.18,Songs,,0,0,0,,and then gentle the next?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.18,0:05:13.33,Songs,,0,0,0,,As long as the two of us share this secret
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.33,0:05:18.89,Songs,,0,0,0,,it will be the light that guides you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.89,0:05:23.67,Songs,,0,0,0,,to somewhere in the yet-unknowable future
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:28.11,Songs,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, it's okay to be optimistic
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.11,0:05:32.15,Songs,,0,0,0,,I want to know everything about you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.15,0:05:37.59,Songs,,0,0,0,,hidden deep within those eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.59,0:05:42.85,Songs,,0,0,0,,I can't control these feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:50.01,Songs,,0,0,0,,Piece by piece, my heart is being snatched away
